creator: micknitchell
descriptionHtml:
We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion of plants & produce! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Browse plants & produce in your local area to either swap, buy, or get for free.

• Upload your plants & produce you want to sell, swap, or donate.

• Post on our community forum to ask questions, request to find a plant, identify a plant, or to just say hi!

• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.

• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.

• Message members securely from within the app.

• Instantly connect with users willing to swap if both of you like each other's plants or produce that are labeled swap or free.

• Build a reputation with our rating system.

• Met someone at an event or farmers market? Scan their QR code to instantly connect and get a list of their inventory while staying in touch afterwards.

• User our map feature for a visual representation of people in your area willing to exchange.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
* Allow link sharing without account
* New sign up flow

We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion of plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Browse for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either swap, buy, or get for free.

• Upload an item you want to swap, sell, or donate.

• Post on our community forum to ask questions, request to find a plant, identify a plant, or to just say hi!

• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.

• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.

• Message members securely from within the app.

• Instantly connect with users willing to swap if both of you like each other's inventory that are labeled swap or free.

• Build a reputation with our rating system.

• Met someone at an event or farmers market? Scan their QR code to instantly connect within the app.

• Use our map feature for a visual representation of people in your area

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Fix inventory upload process
• Fix filters not selecting for market
• New home screen design
• New community posting layout
• Messages associated with inventory
• More market filters
• More community topics
• Fix for adding inventory price >= $1,000
• Bug fixes

We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion of plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Browse for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either swap, buy, or get for free.

• Upload an item you want to swap, sell, or donate.

• Post on our community forum to ask questions, request to find a plant, identify a plant, or to just say hi!

• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.

• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.

• Message members securely from within the app.

• Instantly connect with users willing to swap if both of you like each other's inventory that are labeled swap or free.

• Build a reputation with our rating system.

• Met someone at an event or farmers market? Scan their QR code to instantly connect within the app.

• Use our map feature for a visual representation of people in your area

title: Blossm - Social Plant Market

creator: Blossm LLC
descriptionHtml:
We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion for plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Shop for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either buy, trade, or get for free.
• Upload an item you want to sell, trade, or donate.
• Post on our community forum to ask questions, find plant clippings, identify plants, or to just say hi!
• Get notified when new items matching your wishlist are posted.
• Use our map feature to find plant friends nearby.
• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.
• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.
• Message members securely from within the app.
• Build a reputation with our rating system.

What can I find?
• Rare and collectable houseplants and plant clippings such as the Monstera Albo, Monstera Thai Constellation, Philodendron Pink Princess, and Philodendron Florida Beauty.
• A supportive plant community excited to share tips, tricks, and techniques to help with plant care and identification.
• Free plants, clippings, pots, planters, supplies, and accessories.
• A safe place to buy, sell, trade and swap plants within your own neighborhood and in other communities throughout the US!

Welcome to our growing community!

Follow us on social media:
https://www.facebook.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.instagram.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.tiktok.com/@blossmplantswap
https://www.twitter.com/@blossmllc

title: Blossm - Social Plant Market

creator: Blossm LLC
descriptionHtml:
We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion for plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Shop for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either buy, trade, or get for free.
• Upload an item you want to sell, trade, or donate.
• Post on our community forum to ask questions, find plant clippings, identify plants, or to just say hi!
• Get notified when new items matching your wishlist are posted.
• Use our map feature to find plant friends nearby.
• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.
• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.
• Message members securely from within the app.
• Build a reputation with our rating system.

What can I find?
• Rare and collectable houseplants and plant clippings such as the Monstera Albo, Monstera Thai Constellation, Philodendron Pink Princess, and Philodendron Florida Beauty.
• A supportive plant community excited to share tips, tricks, and techniques to help with plant care and identification.
• Free plants, clippings, pots, planters, supplies, and accessories.
• A safe place to buy, sell, trade and swap plants within your own neighborhood and in other communities throughout the US!

Welcome to our growing community!

Follow us on social media:
https://www.facebook.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.instagram.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.tiktok.com/@blossmplantswap
https://www.twitter.com/@blossmllc

We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion for plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Shop for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either buy, trade, or get for free.
• Upload an item you want to sell, trade, or donate.
• Post on our community forum to ask questions, find plant clippings, identify plants, or to just say hi!
• Get notified when new items matching your wishlist are posted.
• Use our map feature to find plant friends nearby.
• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.
• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.
• Message members securely from within the app.
• Build a reputation with our rating system.

What can I find?
• Rare and collectable houseplants and plant clippings such as the Monstera Albo, Monstera Thai Constellation, Philodendron Pink Princess, and Philodendron Florida Beauty.
• A supportive plant community excited to share tips, tricks, and techniques to help with plant care and identification.
• Free plants, clippings, pots, planters, supplies, and accessories.
• A safe place to buy, sell, trade and swap plants within your own neighborhood and in other communities throughout the US!

Welcome to our growing community!

Follow us on social media:
https://www.facebook.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.instagram.com/blossmplantswap
https://www.tiktok.com/@blossmplantswap
https://www.twitter.com/@blossmllc

title:

2.4.1

creator: Blossm, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
We want to revolutionize the way you connect to people in the community through a shared passion for plants! Our team of quirky green-thumbed enthusiasts have dedicated an immense amount of time and effort to create a way to do this. We hope you will fulfill all your horticultural desires and make this world a greener place!

How it works:

• Shop for plants or other garden related items in your local area to either buy, trade, or get for free.
• Upload an item you want to sell, trade, or donate.
• Post on our community forum to ask questions, find plant clippings, identify plants, or to just say hi!
• Get notified when new items matching your wishlist are posted.
• Use our map feature to find plant friends nearby.
• Search our plant care database and find out how to maintain your new plant baby.
• Get to know your community by exchanging locally.
• Message members securely from within the app.
• Build a reputation with our rating system.

What can I find?
• Rare and collectable houseplants and plant clippings such as the Monstera Albo, Monstera Thai Constellation, Philodendron Pink Princess, and Philodendron Florida Beauty.
• A supportive plant community excited to share tips, tricks, and techniques to help with plant care and identification.
• Free plants, clippings, pots, planters, supplies, and accessories.
• A safe place to buy, sell, trade and swap plants within your own neighborhood and in other communities throughout the US!

Welcome to our growing community!
